The '''Flutterbird Diner''' was a diner in [[Grid 17]] of the [[Southern Underground/Legends|Southern Underground]] of [[Galactic City/Legends|Imperial City]].

[[Memah Roothes]] and [[Neet Alamant]] discussed plans for her to move to a new Imperial-controlled location where she could set up shop for a new [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]], which turned out to be the first [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]].

